= Introduction

== How to Use Abbreviations

This is how to call a abbreviation such as @cpu for the first time.
After that it will look different: @cpu.

It is also call it using a different syntax: #gls("cpu").

And for plurals: #glspl("cpu").

== How to Use Glossary Entries

Glossary entries can be called the same way: @freedom or #gls("freedom").

It is also possible to call plurals: #glspl("freedom").